opinions.text:
ORDER
PER CURIAM.
AND NOW, this 3rd day of October, 2012, the Commonwealth’s application for emergency relief is hereby DENIED. The Prothonotary is directed to set a briefing schedule.
opinions.author: PER CURIAM.
